@@yMeasured Response@@W                                    Sentinel level 30

Passive skill. After a successful parry or dodge, chance to deliver an
automatic counter-strike at 75% weapon damage. The proc also generates
+1 testimony mark (+2 during Ninth Descent).

Proc rate: WIS * 2 percent (44% at WIS 22).

Unlike Counter (CON 22 racial passive), Measured Response fires only on
parry and dodge (not block) and deals reduced damage — but it generates
testimony, creating a defensive feedback loop: avoid, counter-hit, build
toward verdict.

See also: @@msentinel testimony verdict@@W
